blog.title: THE KING OF TIELAND
blog.description: Mr. Merenda is a high school science teacher bringing you Fun Facts from comics, movies, TV, video games, and more every weekday!  He also boasts an impressive collection of over 500 TIES, which along with his many collectibles, are on display for you right here!

summary: As another school year comes to a close, this friendly neighborhood science teacher must leave behind the Spider-Man Fun Facts....
caption:
As another school year comes to a close, this friendly neighborhood science teacher must leave behind the Spider-Man Fun Facts.  But with great power comes a great responsibility to continue the trivia! Keep an eye out for a special Summer Series of Fun Facts beginning in two weeks, with the topic being revealed on Sunday, June 9!

Also, stay tuned for the announcement of next season’s Fun Facts theme on Saturday, August 3! If you think I’m getting tired of doing them, don’t worry… I can do this all day 😉!  And as always, keep an eye out for more noteworthy neckwear from yours truly, the King of Tieland 👔
